title: Mendelssohn - Symphony No. 2 - Abbado, LSO
description:
Mendelssohn: Symphony No. 2, "Hymn of Praise".

Mendelssohn's epic Second Symphony, recorded by Connell (soprano), Mattila (soprano), Blochwitz (tenor), the London Symphony Chorus, and the London Symphony orchestra under Claudio Abbado, released by DG in 1985. Even if you're a fan of Karajan's version, you might come to like this one more-I know I do.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
